Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來戒指的束縛也撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些夜之愛子越來越脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是智世的使魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:01:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你先回去她的影子裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 別發呆了 荊棘之子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡時間流逝比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暫時過來那一側吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且也不可能給人類醫生看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 我會離開一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前來這裡時 你拒絕進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次卻是我帶你進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個半成品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半吊子難聞的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別這麼火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題的 最近來了個好醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然比較古怪就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在還不能起床
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我替你拆掉眼睛上的繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是妖精之國中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個叫蟻冢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 喝下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的身體滋生了太多魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血管和皮膚承受不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然暫時有那根魔繩抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的醫院明明也能做妥善的處置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精王真愛亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只因為他想叫你們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初次見面 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是從小與人類的小孩交換
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由人類撫養的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「調換兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎你來 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然還有臉來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}丘之防人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你養的孩子還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農把她帶走了 應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你們的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孩子有生命危險 當然要幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滿身都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們果然應該住在這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女王 這可不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是我的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精們也會像人類或動物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因病或是年老而虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問艾利亞斯在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他在隨傳隨到的地方 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽說他是你的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們能夠互相溝通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一側的生物在很多問題上 與人類沒有共識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其說是丈夫 更像魔法的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就當作是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏納罕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只過了三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說過 病人是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是夜之愛子 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是重傷患者 別隨便碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是啊 夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天我煮了月夜菇湯 你要早點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉吵到你了 他是我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本是人類 和我調換在這邊長大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被調換後 我們都在對方的世界生活了半個世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半個世紀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}普通的人類要是一直待在這邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不再是人類 而會變成別的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的世界會毒害心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心中累積的毒素 總有一天會侵蝕身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算你沒事 智世也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那孩子更接近我們這邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你真為她著想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就應該讓她拋棄人類的身份 才更能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}否則 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定很快會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我曾經一直以為自己是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在人類世界的醫院工作過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卻被人類討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時 夏納罕過來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我現在才在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被人討厭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直不會衰老 就會讓人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對異類感到恐懼 是弱者的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做著我的工作 努力過好每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼好心虛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水池？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡的水有助於恢復傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少要先把表面的傷口治好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會刺痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像很冷 又好像很暖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以會無條件被夜之愛子吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我非常討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼吸…不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然還不太懂人類的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我想去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們總是偷偷可憐我 嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然人類會懼怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是接受我的 卻又總是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你可別低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要挺起胸膛 看好前方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望她 能夠以人類的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生靈的內心 也就是意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有時候會成為無比強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要想活下去 你甚至能起死回生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特別是在這邊的世界 這一點更加顯著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 就算流的血量足以致死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你卻沒有一絲想要活下去的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你的傷口才一直難以癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 你剛才抵抗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以不管你多麼不想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也要救活你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我希望你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傷口癒合了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏農
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 我會離開一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快看 是報喪女妖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓她靜靜吧 多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憑依的家人不在了的傷心女人太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別待在這裡了 去別的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傾聽你聲音的家人已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說那邊的城鎮有很棒的男人在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}報喪女妖在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還想…留在…他們的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那間房子如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家人虔誠又奉守傳統 挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血脈總有斷絕的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但即便一個家崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要有人活著 就還有家的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要還有一個人活著 便會亮起燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不再有照亮你的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次你去守護那個燈火便可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您好比一株銀色的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起消散於泡沫中 這樣更好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不必言謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保護弱小 是我們守護者的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再會 報喪女妖…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以自己走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 真的讓我很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道自己真的嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你還活著 我就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬上要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩側的時間流逝不一樣 會有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好冷 腳要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍等 我去點暖爐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 家裡好像不太一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 不好意思回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到已經冬天了 我都有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們回來了
Comment: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:33.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:37.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:47.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:57.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:04.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:10.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:23.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:29.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:35.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:42.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:50.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:33.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:37.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:47.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:57.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:04.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:10.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:23.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:29.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:35.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:42.10,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:50.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}我們卻仍在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和魔法使共同度過的第一個聖誕節到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在年末倫敦的喧囂鬧市中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少女又見到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們今天去挑禮物吧
